⚙️ Setup & Installation
1️⃣ Clone the repository
bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/saferoute-ai.git
cd saferoute-ai
2️⃣ Install dependencies
bash
Copy
Edit
pip install -r requirements.txt
3️⃣ Set up Google Vertex AI
Make sure you have a Google Cloud Project with Vertex AI API enabled.

Set your GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS environment variable:

bash
Copy
Edit
export GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS="path/to/your/service-account.json"
4️⃣ Run the server
bash
Copy
Edit
python app.py
Server runs at: http://127.0.0.1:5000/

💡 How It Works
User enters a question in the chat box.

(Optional) Click Ask with Location to include GPS coordinates.

Backend sends question (and location if available) to Google Vertex AI Gemini 2.5 Pro.

AI returns a brief safety-focused response in under 3 sentences.

